thread.title: BRIEF-SJM Holdings Posts FY Gaming Revenue Of HK$41.29 BLN

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-SJM Holdings Posts FY Gaming Revenue Of HK$41.29 BLN
text:
Feb 28 (Reuters) - SJM Holdings Ltd:
* FY GAMING REVENUE HK$ 41.29 BILLION VERSUS HK$41.27 BILLION
* FY NET PROFIT HK$1.96 BILLION VERSUS HK$ 2.33 BILLION ‍​ * ‍RECOMMENDS PAYMENT OF A FINAL DIVIDEND OF HK15 CENTS PER ORDINARY SHARE OF COMPANY​
* FY GAMING REVENUES FROM VIP GAMING OPERATIONS HK$19.88 BILLION VERSUS HK$19.93 BILLION
* FY GAMING REVENUE FROM MASS MARKET TABLE GAMING OPERATIONS HK$20.58 BILLION VERSUS HK$20.44 BILLION Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
